1.title: Twinvasion
1.plot: In this groundbreaking new competition show, 12 sets of identical twins compete to find out who has the greatest "twintuition," with the winners splitting a grand prize of $222,222.22. As the competition begins, the twins are shocked to learn that they will be split up and live separately for the duration of the game.

2.title: Twinstinct
2.plot: Love is in the air and Torian is crushing on Kristina, but will Kristina return his affections, or see it as an opportunity? Meanwhile, Spencer and Skyler are having a bromance with another set of twins, but it might be their downfall.

3.title: Twinstigate
3.plot: The drama heats up as challenge twinners get to cross between the houses and insults turn to rage. Brothers Spencer and Skyler navigate some playful sexual harassment from Sisters Roxanne and Nicole.

4.title: Twinsanity
4.plot: A prank pulled by Tre and Torian could end up having huge consequences on the competition going forward. Meanwhile, one set of twins come up with a risky plan to volunteer to go into the Twin Off. Also, fireworks erupt as two sets of twins finally face off.

5.title: Twintastrophy
5.plot: The aftermath of an epic confrontation forces the twinsets to take sides and puts the future of two sets of twins in jeopardy. Also, Skyler and Spencer contemplate making moves on their crushes in the house, and new alliances are formed after the results of a surprising twin off.

6.title: Twinipulation
6.plot: Desperate to avoid the Twin Off, brothers Adam and Cory continue manipulating people in a power position. But it starts to fall apart once everyone becomes aware of their sneaky ways. A fight erupts when Torian confronts Cory.

7.title: Twinfection
7.plot: Kamila tries to manipulate Winston to help her in the game, but lashes out when she finds out he might be betraying her. Winston's brother Bennett tries to break the hold Kamila has on him. The Twin Off has the most surprising outcome yet.

8.title: Twin Job
8.plot: Weeks of separation is causing some twinsets to crack and Le and Ji want to go home. Meanwhile the loyalty between Torian and Kristina is tested, and Shawn sneaks in the middle to give Torian a hand, literally.

9.title: Twinwreck
9.plot: Torian and Shawn deal with the fallout and consequences of their hook up. Meanwhile their siblings Tre and Claire fear they may be the next to go home because of the drama. Spencer and Skyler have trouble picturing their future apart from each other.

10.title: Twinception
10.plot: As the competition gets closer to the end, the remaining twins are put through the toughest and most grueling challenge yet. Then, everything changes as they are treated to a huge twist; they will all be moving into the same house together!

11.title: Twinners
11.plot: In this season finale, the last three sets of twins must survive one more challenge and two Twin Offs to earn the $222,222 prize.There are no more votes, so Kristina and Kamila come clean about having manipulated Torian through the entire competition.

imdb.plot outline: Twelve pairs of identical twins battle in this reality show. Each week the twins must work with their sibling to win challenges that provide immunity from being voted off by the other competitors. The whole time the contestants live together in two separate but identical "houses" (with each twin being separated), unless they win a challenge which entitles them to move freely between the two houses for a day. At the end of each episode, the two sets of twins with the most votes face off against each other answering questions testing how well they know their sibling, and the losing team goes home. At the end of the season the last remaining team wins $222,222.22 in cash.
